B.ti=new A.bb(B.fK,["A draught! Close the door!","The climbing kitten tore the curtain down! Curtains are a cat climbing wall \u2014 fasten the rails well.","The door swung open! Close it before someone escapes!","The cat escaped!!! The owner is panicking and calling the pet rescue service\u2026","The runaway is back in a carrier. Watch doors and windows \u2014 and microchip your pets!","A CAT'S DAY","A comic-style trainer for future cat owners","PLAY","Settings","Cat care guide","Settings","Sound effects","Background music",'"Kitten on the Keys" \xb7 "The Entertainer" (ragtime, public domain)',"\u042f\u0437\u044b\u043a / Language","Back","Cat care guide","Your day with Misty and kitten Biscuit lasts 10 minutes \u2014 morning to night.\n\n\u2022 BOWL: cats eat 2\u20133 times a day. See a food bubble \u2014 tap the bowls to feed.\n\u2022 LITTER BOX: clean it after use. A cat refuses a dirty box and will leave a puddle right next to it!\n\u2022 PLAY: kittens need frequent play, adults at least twice a day. Tap the toy basket.\n\u2022 CLAWS: scratching is natural! If a cat attacks the sofa or wallpaper, stop it with a tap and offer the scratching post.\n\u2022 TABLE & LAMP: cats love pushing things off. Be quick!\n\u2022 AFFECTION: pet the cats \u2014 tap a cat when it asks for attention.\n\u2022 BIRDS: bird-watching is cat TV. Let them enjoy it!\n\nComplete tasks in time or the cats will start YELLING. Good luck!","Paused","Resume","Restart","Main menu","Score","Time","Tasks","Feed the cats","Clean the litter box","Play with the cats","Pet","Stop the mischief!","Doorbell \u2014 open the door!","Fetch the mouse from under the sofa","Tip: a scratching post saves your furniture. Everybody wins!","Tip: feed cats on a schedule, 2\u20133 times a day.","Tip: a dirty litter box is the #1 cause of accidents.","Tip: 15 minutes of play a day keeps boredom-mischief away.","Tip: cats need affection too. But only when THEY want it.",'A box! Cat logic: "If I fits \u2014 I sits."',"Bird-watching is cat TV. Great for their minds!","Nobody at the door.","Pick up shards right away \u2014 cats can get hurt!","Evening zoomies are normal! Cats burn off energy.","Cats sleep 12\u201316 hours a day. Never wake them \u2014 it is sacred.","Thunderstorm! Cats fear thunder \u2014 let them hide, it is normal.","A fly got in! The best free cat exercise machine.","Cats love knocking pots off. Keep plants away from edges \u2014 and check they are not toxic to cats!","A puddle?! The cat refused the dirty litter box. Clean it in time!","CRASH!","MEOW!","MEE-OW-W!!!","purrr\u2026","scritch-scratch","DING!","KA-BOOM!","OOPS\u2026","NO!","zzz\u2026","Misty","Biscuit","Morning","Day","Evening","Night","DAY SURVIVED!","THE CATS ARE NOT AMUSED\u2026","Tasks completed","Failed","Things ruined","What you learned:","Feed on schedule","Keep the litter box clean","Play every day","Redirect claws to the post","Respect cat rituals","Play again","Purr-fect cat owner! 3 stars!","Great! The cats are mostly pleased.","Not bad, but there is room to grow.","The cats are on strike. Try again!","Morning! Misty and Biscuit are already awake.\nTap objects and cats to take care of them.\nSurvive the day \u2014 10 minutes!","Start the day","Mood","How to play:","\ud83c\udf57 Bowls (left) \u2014 feed","\ud83e\uddf9 Litter box (by the door) \u2014 clean","\ud83e\uddf6 Toy basket \u2014 play","\ud83d\udc3e A cat \u2014 pet it or stop mischief","\ud83d\udc46 Or tap a task card \u2014 the owner does it himself","tap the bowls","tap the litter box","tap the toy basket","tap the cat","tap the naughty cat!","tap the door","tap the sofa"],t.W)
B.IN=new A.bb(B.fK,["Tocht! Doe de deur dicht!","De klimmende kitten heeft het gordijn eraf getrokken! Gordijnen zijn een kattenklimwand \u2014 bevestig de rails stevig.","De deur is opengewaaid! Doe hem dicht voordat iemand ontsnapt!","De kat is ontsnapt!!! Het baasje belt in paniek de dierenambulance\u2026","De weggelopen kat is terug in een reismand. Let op deuren en ramen \u2014 en chip je huisdieren!","KATTENDAG","Een striptrainer voor toekomstige kattenbaasjes","SPELEN","Instellingen","Verzorgingsgids","Instellingen","Geluidseffecten","Achtergrondmuziek",'"Kitten on the Keys" \xb7 "The Entertainer" (ragtime, publiek domein)',"\u042f\u0437\u044b\u043a / Language","Terug","Verzorgingsgids voor katten","Je dag met Minoes en kitten Poekie duurt 10 minuten \u2014 van ochtend tot nacht.\n\n\u2022 VOERBAK: katten eten 2\u20133 keer per dag. Zie je een voerballon \u2014 tik op de bakjes om te voeren.\n\u2022 KATTENBAK: maak hem schoon na gebruik. Een kat weigert een vieze bak en laat er een plasje naast achter!\n\u2022 SPELEN: kittens willen vaak spelen, volwassen katten minstens twee keer per dag. Tik op de speelgoedmand.\n\u2022 NAGELS: krabben is natuurlijk! Krabt een kat aan de bank of het behang, stop haar met een tik en bied de krabpaal aan.\n\u2022 TAFEL & LAMP: katten duwen graag dingen eraf. Wees er snel bij!\n\u2022 AANDACHT: aai de katten \u2014 tik op een kat als ze om aandacht vraagt.\n\u2022 VOGELTJES: vogels kijken is katten-tv. Laat ze genieten!\n\nVoer taken op tijd uit, anders gaan de katten MAUWEN. Succes!","Pauze","Verder","Opnieuw","Hoofdmenu","Punten","Tijd","Taken","Voer de katten","Maak de kattenbak schoon","Speel met de katten","Aai","Stop het kattenkwaad!","De deurbel \u2014 doe open!","Pak de muis onder de bank vandaan","Tip: een krabpaal redt je meubels. Iedereen blij!","Tip: voer katten volgens schema, 2\u20133 keer per dag.","Tip: een vieze kattenbak is oorzaak nr. 1 van ongelukjes.","Tip: 15 minuten spelen per dag voorkomt kattenkwaad uit verveling.","Tip: katten hebben ook aandacht nodig. Maar alleen als ZIJ dat willen.",'Een doos! Kattenlogica: "Pas ik erin \u2014 dan zit ik erin."',"Vogels kijken is katten-tv. Goed voor hun kopje!","Er is niemand aan de deur.","Ruim scherven meteen op \u2014 katten kunnen zich bezeren!","Avond-zoomies zijn normaal! Katten razen hun energie eruit.","Katten slapen 12\u201316 uur per dag. Nooit wakker maken \u2014 dat is heilig.","Onweer! Katten zijn bang voor de donder \u2014 laat ze schuilen, dat is normaal.","Er vliegt een vlieg binnen! Het beste gratis fitnessapparaat voor katten.","Katten duwen graag potten om. Zet planten niet op de rand \u2014 en check of ze niet giftig zijn voor katten!","Een plasje?! De kat weigerde de vieze bak. Maak de bak op tijd schoon!","KNAL!","MIAUW!","MI-AAA-UW!!!","prrr\u2026","krits-krats","DING!","KA-BOEM!","OEPS\u2026","NEE!","zzz\u2026","Minoes","Poekie","Ochtend","Middag","Avond","Nacht","DAG OVERLEEFD!","DE KATTEN ZIJN NIET BLIJ\u2026","Taken voltooid","Mislukt","Kapotte spullen","Wat je hebt geleerd:","Voeren volgens schema","De kattenbak schoon houden","Elke dag spelen","Nagels naar de krabpaal leiden","Kattenrituelen respecteren","Nog een keer","Purr-fect kattenbaasje! 3 sterren!","Geweldig! De katten zijn bijna helemaal tevreden.","Niet slecht, maar er valt nog wat te leren.","De katten staken. Probeer het nog eens!","Goedemorgen! Minoes en Poekie zijn al wakker.\nTik op voorwerpen en katten om voor ze te zorgen.\nHou de dag vol \u2014 10 minuten!","Begin de dag","Humeur","Zo speel je:","\ud83c\udf57 Voerbakjes (links) \u2014 voeren","\ud83e\uddf9 Kattenbak (bij de deur) \u2014 schoonmaken","\ud83e\uddf6 Speelgoedmand \u2014 spelen","\ud83d\udc3e Een kat \u2014 aaien of kattenkwaad stoppen","\ud83d\udc46 Of tik op een taakkaart \u2014 het baasje doet het zelf","tik op de voerbakjes","tik op de kattenbak","tik op de speelgoedmand","tik op de kat","tik op de ondeugende kat!","tik op de deur","tik op de bank"],t.W)
B.IP=new A.bb(B.fK,["\xa1Corriente de aire! \xa1Cierra la puerta!","\xa1El gatito escalador arranc\xf3 la cortina! Las cortinas son un roc\xf3dromo felino \u2014 sujeta bien las barras.","\xa1La puerta se abri\xf3 de golpe! \xa1Ci\xe9rrala antes de que alguien se escape!","\xa1\xa1\xa1El gato se escap\xf3!!! El due\xf1o llama en p\xe1nico al servicio de rescate\u2026","El fugitivo vuelve en un transport\xedn. Vigila puertas y ventanas \u2014 \xa1y pon microchip a tus mascotas!","EL D\xcdA DEL GATO","Un entrenador de c\xf3mic para futuros due\xf1os de gatos","JUGAR","Ajustes","Gu\xeda de cuidados","Ajustes","Efectos de sonido","M\xfasica de fondo",'"Kitten on the Keys" \xb7 "The Entertainer" (ragtime, dominio p\xfablico)',"\u042f\u0437\u044b\u043a / Language","Atr\xe1s","Gu\xeda de cuidados felinos","Tu d\xeda con Michi y el gatito Bigotes dura 10 minutos \u2014 de la ma\xf1ana a la noche.\n\n\u2022 COMEDERO: los gatos comen 2\u20133 veces al d\xeda. \xbfVes un globo de comida? Toca los comederos para alimentarlos.\n\u2022 ARENERO: l\xedmpialo despu\xe9s de cada uso. \xa1Un gato rechaza el arenero sucio y dejar\xe1 un charco al lado!\n\u2022 JUEGO: los gatitos necesitan jugar a menudo; los adultos, al menos dos veces al d\xeda. Toca la cesta de juguetes.\n\u2022 U\xd1AS: \xa1ara\xf1ar es natural! Si un gato ataca el sof\xe1 o el papel pintado, detenlo con un toque y ofr\xe9cele el rascador.\n\u2022 MESA Y L\xc1MPARA: a los gatos les encanta tirar cosas. \xa1Date prisa!\n\u2022 CARI\xd1O: acaricia a los gatos \u2014 toca a un gato cuando pida atenci\xf3n.\n\u2022 PAJARITOS: mirar p\xe1jaros es la tele de los gatos. \xa1D\xe9jalos disfrutar!\n\nCompleta las tareas a tiempo o los gatos empezar\xe1n a MAULLAR. \xa1Suerte!","Pausa","Continuar","Reiniciar","Men\xfa principal","Puntos","Tiempo","Tareas","Da de comer a los gatos","Limpia el arenero","Juega con los gatos","Acaricia a","\xa1Det\xe9n la travesura!","\xa1El timbre \u2014 abre la puerta!","Saca el rat\xf3n de debajo del sof\xe1","Consejo: el rascador salva tus muebles. \xa1Todos contentos!","Consejo: alimenta a los gatos con horario, 2\u20133 veces al d\xeda.","Consejo: un arenero sucio es la causa n\xba 1 de accidentes.","Consejo: 15 minutos de juego al d\xeda evitan travesuras por aburrimiento.","Consejo: los gatos tambi\xe9n necesitan cari\xf1o. Pero solo cuando ELLOS quieren.",'\xa1Una caja! L\xf3gica felina: "Si quepo \u2014 me siento".',"Mirar p\xe1jaros es la tele de los gatos. \xa1Buen\xedsimo para su mente!","No hay nadie en la puerta.","\xa1Recoge los trozos enseguida \u2014 los gatos pueden hacerse da\xf1o!","\xa1La locura nocturna es normal! Los gatos queman energ\xeda.","Los gatos duermen 12\u201316 horas al d\xeda. No los despiertes \u2014 es sagrado.","\xa1Tormenta! Los gatos temen los truenos \u2014 d\xe9jalos esconderse, es normal.","\xa1Entr\xf3 una mosca! El mejor gimnasio gratuito para gatos.","A los gatos les encanta tirar macetas. No pongas plantas al borde \u2014 \xa1y comprueba que no sean t\xf3xicas para gatos!","\xbf\xa1Un charco!? El gato rechaz\xf3 el arenero sucio. \xa1L\xedmpialo a tiempo!","\xa1CRASH!","\xa1MIAU!","\xa1\xa1\xa1MIA-A-AU!!!","prrr\u2026","ras-ras","\xa1DING!","\xa1BUUUM!","UPS\u2026","\xa1NO!","zzz\u2026","Michi","Bigotes","Ma\xf1ana","D\xeda","Tarde","Noche","\xa1D\xcdA SUPERADO!","LOS GATOS NO EST\xc1N CONTENTOS\u2026","Tareas completadas","Falladas","Cosas rotas","Lo que has aprendido:","Alimentar con horario","Mantener limpio el arenero","Jugar cada d\xeda","Dirigir las u\xf1as al rascador","Respetar los rituales felinos","Jugar otra vez","\xa1Due\xf1o purr-fecto! \xa13 estrellas!","\xa1Genial! Los gatos est\xe1n casi del todo contentos.","No est\xe1 mal, pero a\xfan puedes mejorar.","Los gatos se han declarado en huelga. \xa1Int\xe9ntalo de nuevo!","\xa1Buenos d\xedas! Michi y Bigotes ya est\xe1n despiertos.\nToca los objetos y los gatos para cuidarlos.\n\xa1Aguanta el d\xeda \u2014 10 minutos!","Empezar el d\xeda","\xc1nimo","C\xf3mo se juega:","\ud83c\udf57 Comederos (izquierda) \u2014 alimentar","\ud83e\uddf9 Arenero (junto a la puerta) \u2014 limpiar","\ud83e\uddf6 Cesta de juguetes \u2014 jugar","\ud83d\udc3e Un gato \u2014 acariciar o detener travesuras","\ud83d\udc46 O toca una tarjeta de tarea \u2014 el due\xf1o lo hace solo","toca los comederos","toca el arenero","toca la cesta de juguetes","toca al gato","\xa1toca al gato travieso!","toca la puerta","toca el sof\xe1"],t.W)
